    a(href='/') page d'accueil

  h3 Liste des repas solides :
  ul
    - each rep, i in repas
      li
        | Menu
        = rep.menu
        br
        | Date et heure
        = rep.dob
        br
        form(action='/repas/#{rep._id}/edit', method='post', name= 'deleterepas', enctype='application/x-www-form-urlencoded')
